     C/EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      ** VALIDATION - Local Industry Code
      *****************************************************************
     C     LICDV         BEGSR
                                                                                              CSD094
      ** If CSD094 is installed, Local Industry Code is mandatory                             CSD094
                                                                                              CSD094
     C     CSD094        IFEQ      'Y'                                                        CSD094
     C     DDLICD        ANDEQ     *BLANK                                                     CSD094
     C                   MOVE      'N'           DDLICDOK                                     CSD094
     C                   ADD       1             Idx                                          CSD094
     C                   MOVEL     'DDLICD'      FldNamXAr(Idx)                               CSD094
     C                   MOVEL     'USS0917'     MsgIdXAr(Idx)                                CSD094
     C                   ENDIF                                                                CSD094

      ** If local industry code is entered, must be on file
     C     DDLICD        IFNE      *BLANK
     C     DDLICD        CHAIN     LOCINDUS                           90
     C     *IN90         IFEQ      '1'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           DDLICDOK
     C                   ADD       1             Idx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDLICD'      FldNamXAr(Idx)
     C                   MOVEL     'USR0035'     MsgIdXAr(Idx)
     C                   ENDIF
     C                   ENDIF
