      * Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Local Industry Code - OK
     C                   PARM                    DDLICDOK          1
